  <brief_title>Long-Term Safety and Efficacy Evaluation of EPI-743 in Children With Leigh Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>EPI743-13-023: Long-Term Safety and Efficacy Evaluation of EPI-743 in Children With Leigh Syndrome</official_title>
