  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      EPI-743 in Leigh syndrome subjects that participated in previous EPI743-12-002 study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To monitor the long-term safety and neurodevelopmental effects of EPI-743 on children who
      complete the EPI743-12-002 placebo controlled trial.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
